    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of well-documented care and consistent maintenance. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical of a car that has been driven responsibly. Inside, the interior is remarkably clean; the premium upholstery shows light bolstering wear on the driver's side but remains free of tears or stains. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. The engine idles quietly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes were serviced just 3,000 miles ago. It sits on a set of Michelin tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This has been a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle, stored in a climate-controlled garage. We have the full service log available for review, confirming regular oil changes and scheduled inspections. It is a reliable, turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner.",
